{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "29", "m": "03", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "16", "M": "22", "S": "00"}}, "news": [{"title": "Inaugurated in haste? Wayanad township project slows to a crawl", "para": "Newly built houses for Wayanad landslide survivors remain unoccupied. Inaugurated nearly a month ago, pending plumbing and sewage works prevent families from moving in. The delay has ignited political debate, with the opposition accusing the government of an election stunt. The project faces worker shortages as migrant laborers return home for elections.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/political-controversy-erupts-over-incomplete-wayanad-township-project/129881880?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-108778/129881880.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Hyderabad civic body locks over 100 big properties over tax dues", "para": "Hyderabad civic body is cracking down on major property tax defaulters, sealing over 100 commercial properties to recover hundreds of crores. High-profile establishments like Katriya Hotel and Aurora College face significant liabilities. The drive now includes vacant lands, with warnings of property auctions for non-payment. A One-Time Settlement scheme offers a 90% interest waiver.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/hyderabad-seals-over-100-major-properties-amidst-tax-crisis/129881661?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-41312/129881661.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}, {"title": "Over 1,000 flats to be made in Prayagraj for urban poor under PMAY", "para": "Prayagraj authorities are set to build over 1,000 flats under Pradhan Mantri Awas Yojana Phase II. The Prayagraj Development Authority is identifying land for the project. Several locations are shortlisted, and land allocation is expected soon. This initiative will provide housing for economically weaker sections. Nearly 1,000 beneficiaries have already registered online for these upcoming homes.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/prayagraj-to-build-over-1000-affordable-flats-for-urban-poor-under-pmay/129881230?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-31996/129881230.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}]}